tibackuplib (0.8.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add SSH-Server support (lockstep with tibackup 0.8.2): SSHServer model,
    tiConfSSHServers config store, and a rsync-over-SSH backup path in
    tiBackupJob. New sshClient wraps ssh/ssh-keyscan/ssh-keygen with host-key
    pinning and keepalive-bounded transfers.

 -- Rene Hadler <rene@hadler.me>  Thu, 16 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

tibackuplib (0.8.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * initMainConf: default web/bind to 0.0.0.0 on fresh installs so the tibackup
    web UI is reachable over HTTPS on all interfaces (lockstep with tibackup 0.8.1)

 -- Rene Hadler <rene@hadler.me>  Thu, 09 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

